column1: Contains 'g' Schmidt semi-normalized spherical harmonic coefficients for O4 internal field model of Jupiter in gauss (G)
column3: so that each row represents a single n and each column a single m. See https://doi.org/10.1029/JA081i016p02917; note that the original publication used SIII (1957) coordinates
column4: and these values were updated to SIII (1965) coordinates by Acuna et al. (1983)
column5: as reported in Connerney (1992) along with the O6 model: https://core.ac.uk/download/pdf/83644007.pdf
